2701	  restriction map \(\Gamma(M, \top) \to \Gamma(M, D(f))\) exhibits \(\Gamma(M, D(f))\) as the
2702	  localized module \((\mathrm{powers}\,f)^{-1}\,\Gamma(M, \top)\); i.e.\ it is
